# Cursor Rules

# General
- Check `.agents/rules/RULES.md` for standard project constraints.
- This project automates the Antigravity editor via Chrome DevTools Protocol.

# Context
- Entry point: `src/auto-retry.js`
- Payload: `src/injection-payload.js` (runs in browser context)
- Always increment `INJECTION_VERSION` in `injection-payload.js` if you modify its logic.

# Commands
- Test daemon: `npm run start:debug`
- Setup LaunchAgent: `npm run install-agent`
